-to-day through interactions and conversations. In-game dinosaur-themed social media and interactive one-offs make you a part of Fang's life. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1310330/extras/92459d15d918d50f61b5b9fba55bbb55.poster.avif?t=1758723684\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1310330/extras/92459d15d918d50f61b5b9fba55bbb55.webm?t=1758723684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1310330/extras/92459d15d918d50f61b5b9fba55bbb55.mp4?t=1758723684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1310330/extras/932ffe3dee0f87981d49fb79a1022995.webp?t=1758723684\" width=619 height=19 /></span></p>",
